Package zuul.pkg_room

Class Room

  • java.lang.Object
    • zuul.pkg_room.Room
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LockedRoom, TransporterRoom
    public class Room
extends Object
    This room represents a room in the Zuul game. It allows to manipulate the items inside as well as various game mechanics.
    Version:
    06.04.21
    Author:
